<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon"/><title>MiSans</title><meta name="keywords" content="HyperOS,HyperOS Font,小米字体,小米系统字体,MiSans,misans,HyperOS 系统字体,互联网字体,字体,免费商用字体"/><meta name="description" content="MiSans Global 是由小米主导，联合蒙纳字库、汉仪字库共同打造的全球语言字体定制项目。这是一个庞大的字体家族，涵盖 20 多种书写系统，支持 600 多种语言，字符数量超过 10 万个。作为 Xiaomi HyperOS 系统默认字体，我们以简约/清晰，人文/易读，统一的视觉风格为基本原则出发，构建多语言信息体验一致性，旨在帮助为 Xiaomi HyperOS 提供互联的通用体验"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0"/><meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark"/><meta name="next-head-count" content="7"/><link rel="preload" href="/font/_next/static/css/7785a02eb12d9235.css" as="style"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/font/_next/static/css/7785a02eb12d9235.css" data-n-g=""/><noscript data-n-css=""></noscript><script defer="" nomodule="" src="/font/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-c67a75d1b6f99dc8.js"></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/webpack-836f5ed623cabca3.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/framework-8d78bf989db74c8f.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/main-f7f96c2e0d77b825.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-494a3cb137b3805f.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/657-896f4ddacb1db285.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/chunks/pages/download-123385fa78b6a31a.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/p8vjJuMJSWlSX4i0fBbv9/_buildManifest.js" defer=""></script><script src="/font/_next/static/p8vjJuMJSWlSX4i0fBbv9/_ssgManifest.js" defer=""></script></head><body><div id="__next"><nav class="nav-position nav-display nav-width nav-height items-center bg-white/90 transition-all sm:backdrop-blur"><div class="nav-display w-full"><div class="font-sans font-[600] rem:text-[26px] transition-all text-black"></div><div class="relative cursor-pointer text-black rem:h-[20.91px] rem:w-[30.35px] transitio